<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="vp22Dec1938"><font color="red">22 December 1938</font> <i>NLVP</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to Ben Huebsch): Work in Progress is now finished and entirely galleyed. More than half of it is already finally paged and Mr Joyce is in the throws of proof correction. </div>
